# Changelog

## 2026-01-22 - Initial Creation

**RED Phase Evidence:**
- Chariot codebase has `useViewportCulling.ts` with partial phase guards (lines 140-145)
- Existing guards receive phase as prop but don't subscribe to layout events
- No layout instance management patterns documented
- No camera coordination during layout
- Developers implementing hierarchical navigation lack complete coordination guidance

